Prerequisites
=============

To build Zombiepolis you will need
 * Java Development Kit (version 7), get it from http://oracle.com/technetwork/java
 * Apache Ant, get it from http://ant.apache.org


Building the Package
====================

  1. `cd' to the directory containing the package's source code.

  2. Type `ant' to compile the package.


Installing Zombiepolis
======================

To run the program you need the micropolisj.jar file and the graphics directory.
So just copy those to objects to wherever you like.


Running Zombiepolis
===================

Type `java -jar micropolisj.jar` to run the program.

